Interface Period

All Superinterfaces:
Comparable<Period>, Entity<Period>, Named, RaplaObject<Period>
public interface Period
extends Entity<Period>, Comparable<Period>, Named

Most universities and schools are planning for fixed periods/terms rather than arbitrary dates. Rapla provides support for this periods.
